headline: AI Stocks Among 5 Leaders Near Buy Points As Trump Rally Wavers
summary: Two software makers embracing AI are among five stocks near buy points as the Trump rally wavers. Just one is in a buy zone now.

headline: J.P. Morgan Says These 2 Stocks Are Top Picks for 2025
summary: With 2025 on the horizon, investors are sharpening their focus on the year ahead, selecting portfolio additions that aim to bring solid returns. “There is reason to be bullish,” says Jordan Jackson, a JPMorgan strategist covering the markets.
